{"id":941438931,"lang":"cpp","lang_name":"C++","time":"7 months, 1 week","timestamp":1682753739,"status":10,"status_display":"Accepted","runtime":"9 ms","url":"/submissions/detail/941438931/","is_pending":"Not Pending","title":"Reverse Vowels of a String","memory":"8 MB","code":"class Solution {\npublic:\n    bool isVowel(char c){\n        return(c=='a'||c=='A'||c=='e'||c=='E'||c=='i'||c=='I'||c=='o'||c=='O'||c=='u'||c=='U');\n    }\n    string reverseVowels(string s) {\n        vector<char> vowels;\n        int j=0;\n        for(char c:s)\n        if(isVowel(c))\n        vowels.push_back(c);\n        for(int i=0;i<s.length();i++)\n        if(isVowel(s[i])){\n            s[i]=vowels[vowels.size()-j-1];\n            j++;\n        }\n        return(s);\n    }\n};","compare_result":"","title_slug":"reverse-vowels-of-a-string","has_notes":false,"flag_type":1}
